OL,10,     Fdifferent approach when he refuses
OL,11,     Fto change. (S4, ep 2)
OL,12,G1045 The Alfred Hitchcock Hour
OL,13,     FThe Cadaver: A college aide
OL,14,     Fborrows a dead female body from
OL,15,     Fthe lab and puts it in his
OL,16,     Froommate's dorm to try and scare
OL,17,     Fhim sober, but the joke becomes
OL,18,     Fdisastrous. (S2, ep 8)
